      "role": "user",
      "content": "That makes sense, thank you. To round out their prep, can you also provide the most common counterarguments used against these specific points? My students really need to see the nuance in the debate—how do people typically respond to the \"rule of law\" and \"social contract\" arguments you just laid out?",
